&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Private practice with no doors and no overhead.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;BetterHelp is one of the world’s largest online therapy platforms for mental health professionals who want to focus on client care — not admin or overhead. You provide the expertise. We handle the rest.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
